reviewText: Good story, acting, etc.  Video quality sub-par.
It would have been better if the film quality was much better.  I was surprised that the resolution of the movie was not good.

'The Big Bluff' suffers from rather poor cinematography and the obvious evil machinations of playboy Rick De Villa. On the other hand, its clever and surprise ending makes up for most the prior dreariness.
visual very poor, cannot watch this DVD. not sure what to do with it now, not sure if I can return.
